---
<section class="cta-section" id="cta">
  <div class="wrap">
    <h2>
      Inscribe tu próxima<br/>
      <span class="italic">generación</span> más rápido.
    </h2>
    <p>Onboarding en 30 minutos. Capacitamos a tu equipo y ponemos a Ada en vivo con el contenido de tu escuela en menos de 24 horas. Mira cómo tu inbox de admisiones se calma — y tu lista caliente se llena.</p>
    <div class="cta-row">
      <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">
        Agenda una demo de 20 minutos
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/></svg>
      </a>
      <a href="#" class="btn btn-ghost-dark">Habla con los fundadores</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .cta-section {
    background: var(--color-ink); color: var(--color-cream);
    position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .cta-section::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse 70% 60% at 50% 0%, rgba(215,242,107,0.12), transparent 60%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .cta-section .wrap { position: relative; z-index: 1; text-align: center; }
  .cta-section h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-sans); font-weight: 500;
    font-size: clamp(40px,7vw,80px);
    line-height: 1; letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    color: var(--color-cream);
  }
  .cta-section h2 .italic { font-family: var(--font-serif); font-style: italic; font-weight: 400; }
  .cta-section p {
    margin-top: 24px; font-size: 18px; color: rgba(242,239,230,0.6);
    max-width: 540px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .cta-row {
    margin-top: 36px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .cta-section .btn-primary {
    background: var(--color-lime); color: var(--color-ink);
  }
  .cta-section .btn-primary:hover {
    background: #E1F88A;
    box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(215,242,107,0.35);
  }
  .btn-ghost-dark {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
    padding: 14px 22px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 500;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: transparent; color: rgba(242,239,230,0.7);
    border: 1px solid rgba(242,239,230,0.2);
    transition: background 0.15s, color 0.15s;
  }
  .btn-ghost-dark:hover { background: rgba(242,239,230,0.08); color: var(--color-cream); }
</style>
